description: Fix issue with cache filenames when assuming a role on Windows (`issue 1063 <https://github.com/aws/aws-cli/issues/1063>`__)
Fix issue when listing Amazon S3 objects containing non-ascii characters in eu-central-1 (`issue 1046 <https://github.com/aws/aws-cli/issues/1046>`__)
Update the ``aws storagegateway`` command to the latest version
Update the ``aws emr`` command to the latest version
Fix script runnner jar to the current region location when ``--enable-debugging`` is specified in the ``aws emr create-cluster`` command
